        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Technology Standards Task Force Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Office of Science and Technology Policy to establish a task force on setting emerging technology standards, to be known as the Emerging Technology Standards-Setting Task Force. </p> <p>The task force shall develop a long-term strategic plan for the United States to lead emerging technology standards-setting processes.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
